		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Temeraire (series)</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about the series of books written by Naomi Novik.  For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Temeraire" title="Temeraire">Temeraire</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:152px;"><a href="/wiki/File:038647-FC50.jpg" class="image" title="U.K. paperback edition cover of Throne of Jade"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/04/038647-FC50.jpg/150px-038647-FC50.jpg" width="150" height="229" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
